sign strategy and direction define and iterate how a brand should be expressed across all our products take responsibility for leading a team of designers in their day to day job - making sure that design and creative concepts are always polished and of the highest quality solve problems conceptually in collaboration with the broader interactive team, including writers, UX/UI designers, and developers work closely with the sales and marketing team to create and execute winning ideas. Requirements Requirements: at least 3 years of experience as a Lead Designer responsible for leading the team of designers and building a team Experience in mentoring fellow designers, encouraging them to take appropriate risks, and providing constructive support, feedback, and critique A minimum of 7+ years of significant experience within user interface design, usability, design research and data-driven design Ability to collaborate with our marketing team to craft compelling stories through copy, video, animation, illustration, and photography Experience in working with designers and product managers to set timeline expectations and create project plans Demonstrate a modern portfolio of work with a proven track record for solving complex UX/UI design problems Fluency in communicating in English Ability to follow the full Product Design Lifecycle Expert knowledge of tools like Invision, Figma and the Adobe CC package Experience building low and high fidelity prototypes of digital products to illustrate functionality (use of Paper, Invision and Principle) Perks: You get to work alongside a group of talented people, all passionate about what they do. Great opportunity to learn about the world of blockchain and cryptocurrencies Remote working, flexible hours Opportunity to work on creatively challenging projects everyday Competitive salary. Please attach a portfolio with at least 5/6 of your best works in your application. Applicants without a portfolio will not be considered. Skills Des